feed.name: Vicente Goetten
feed.messageBody: Latest edition of Trends in Cognitive Sciences reports that stressful experiences like social defeat, exposure to predator odors, sleep deprivation have been shown to decrease the number of new neurons in the hippocampus.

feed.name: Sophie Curtis
feed.messageBody: Scientists have created a new form of hydrogel that can be injected without the need for surgery! These gels can be delivered via syringes with the same effectiveness.

feed.name: Paris Schreiber
feed.messageBody: It may seem bizarre but in the quantum world the future dictates what will happen in the past. This conclusion is the result of a statistical measurement of probabilities in quantum mechanics.
